videos.headline: Darnold gets USC going with long pass completion
videos.description: Sam Darnold connects with Daniel Imatorbhebhe for a big gain to get the Trojans down to the 35-yard line.

videos.headline: Darnold tosses first TD of Pac-12 championship
videos.description: Sam Darnold finds Michael Pittman Jr. in the back of the end zone for the 7-yard score to give USC the lead.

videos.headline: Love answers with rushing TD
videos.description: Bryce Love gets the call for Stanford on the 9-yard line and powers up the middle for the game-tying touchdown.

videos.headline: USC gains 40 on Darnold to Pittman connection
videos.description: USC gets out of a huge hole with the 40-yard pitch-and-catch between Sam Darnold and Michael Pittman Jr.

videos.headline: Darnold tosses 2nd TD against Stanford
videos.description: Sam Darnold swings it out to Tyler Vaughns who stretches over the pylon for the USC touchdown.

videos.headline: Stanford knocking on the door after 42-yard pass
videos.description: K.J. Costello launches a pass downfield and JJ Arcega-Whiteside fights off two defenders to come down with the catch inside the USC 10-yard line.

videos.headline: Stanford punches in 1-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Stanford is able to work quickly downfield and Cameron Scarlett caps off a great drive with a rushing touchdown just before halftime.

videos.headline: Helton: 'Play a little cleaner on offense'
videos.description: After a first half that was riddled with penalties, USC head coach Clay Helton looks to clean up their offense and keep up the strong performance.

videos.headline: Darnold spurs USC to halftime lead
videos.description: Sam Darnold's two touchdown passes gives USC  a slim edge over Stanford at halftime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Darnold spurs USC to halftime lead) 2017/12/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shaw: 'We can't miss tackles'
videos.description: Stanford head coach David Shaw says the Cardinal needs to have more production on offense and less mistakes on defense.

videos.headline: Long pass leads to 1-yard touchdown run for USC
videos.description: Sam Darnold throws a bomb downfield to Steven Mitchell Jr. who makes the grab at the 1-yard line and Ronald Jones II finishes the job with the touchdown run.

videos.headline: Love takes off for 52-yard gain
videos.description: Bryce Love makes a quick cut and flies downfield for a huge chunk of yardage to put Stanford in the red zone.

videos.headline: Stanford with an incredible catch for TD
videos.description: K.J. Costello throws it to the back of the end zone for Kaden Smith who makes the leaping grab and then is able to get one foot down before falling out of bounds.

videos.headline: USC coughs up the football into Stanford's arms
videos.description: Stephen Carr gets hit hard by Alameen Murphy on the carry forcing the fumble and Justin Reid is there to cover up the loose ball.

videos.headline: Stanford gets stuffed on fourth-and-goal
videos.description: USC's defense shows its strength as the Trojans keep Stanford out of the end zone on fourth-and-goal from the 1-yard line.

videos.headline: Darnold escapes pressure and finds Pittman Jr. for 54 yeards
videos.description: Sam Darnold has the pocket collapse on him, almost goes down in the end zone, but is able to get rid of the pass and find a wide open Michael Pittman Jr. who takes off for 54 yards.

videos.headline: Jones II scoots in for 2nd rushing TD of game
videos.description: Ronald Jones Jr. bounces to the outside and fights his way into the end zone for the 8-yard touchdown to put USC up by 10.

videos.headline: Stanford moves quickly with 45-yard pass completion
videos.description: K.J. Costello hurls the ball downfield to JJ Arcega-Whiteside who leaps and makes the grab for a 45-yard gain inside the red zone.

videos.headline: Costello tosses 2nd TD to keep Stanford close
videos.description: K.J. Costello throws a laser to the end zone and Kaden Smith makes a jaw-dropping grab for the score to put pressure on USC.

videos.headline: USC seals the Pac-12 Championship with completion on 4th
videos.description: Sam Darnold rolls out of the pocket and hits Josh Falo for the first down to lock up the Pac-12 championship over Stanford.

videos.headline: Darnold: 'It means the world'
videos.description: Sam Darnold explains why this Pac-12 Championship was a combined effort and how the Trojans got it done.

videos.headline: Helton: 'It was a team effort all the way through'
videos.description: USC head coach Clay Helton says this Trojans team worked hard for this win and deserves to be talked about in the College Football Playoff.

videos.headline: Darnold wins MVP of Pac-12 Championship
videos.description: The USC Trojans are the Pac-12 champions behind Sam Darnold's two touchdown, 325-yard performance.

videos.headline: Helton excited to bring Trojan's victory home
videos.description: USC head coach Clay Helton credits his Trojan family for the Pac-12 Championship win.

videos.headline: Darnold: 'We made a statement here tonight'
videos.description: Pac-12 Championship MVP Sam Darnold joins SVP and explains why this Trojans team has incredible resiliency.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Darnold: 'We made a statement here tonight') 2017/12/01 SC

videos.headline: USC wins first Pac-12 title since 2008
videos.description: Sam Darnold and Ronald Jones II carry USC past Stanford 31-28 to win the Pac-12 championship.

videos.headline: Inside USC's crucial stop
videos.description: USC's goal-line stop against Stanford propels the Trojans to a victory and the Pac 12 title.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Inside USC's crucial stop) 2017/12/1 ESHEET
